songs.title: Make Me Over
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
I spent all my money
I'm home looking bummy, yeah
Will you help me honey?
I wanna go out with some friends
I need some ends

I’ve always been independent
But right now will you do this for me

[Chorus]
Just make me over
Make me over
Make me over

[Verse 2]
It's been fifty twenty, yeah
So glad you're still with me
I don’t want to be alone
No dollars in the bank
Hold my hand or I'll sink

When I get my paycheck
I promise to do something nice
But for now oh just

[Chorus]
Make me over
Make me over
Make me over

[Bridge]
I need a little bit of spending money
I trust in you

[Chorus]
Make me over (make me over)
Make me over (make me over)
Make me over

Yeah yeah yeah
